      "text": "突然押しかけてご迷惑じゃありませんでしたか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope we’re not intruding by visiting so suddenly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2443311055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "サニーピースのみなさんならいつでも大歓迎よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The girls of Sunny Peace are always welcome.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.977800401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skrmam",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-skrmam002.m4a",
      "text": "すぐにおせちとお雑煮を用意するから待っててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just wait for a little and I’ll bring some New Year dishes and rice cake soup.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 32.645736758
    },
    {
